div.p:
5. This Day is claimed by the Lord, as a thing wherein he hath a special Propriety: It's the Lords Day;  
                     •
                  or though he did give Six, yet he reserved a Seventh. And can, or dare, any say, That he discharged that, or dispensed it away from Himself, to any other? If not, it must be His still; and cannot without Sacriledge, be other wayes applyed.
